title: EYL #197 The Netflix for Pets
itunes:title: EYL #197 The Netflix for Pets
description:
In episode 197, we spoke to Amman Ahmed. Amman is the founder of the extremely popular Relax My Dog and Relax My Cat platforms. The platforms have been called the Netflix for pets. #doglovers #pets #business 

This episode focuses on marketing, business growth, and expansion.
